verses.text:
Thus saith the \nd LORD\nd*; For three transgressions of Israel,
and for four, I will not turn away \add the punishment\add* thereof; because they
sold the righteous for silver, and the poor for a pair of shoes;

Come to Beth-el, and transgress; at Gilgal multiply transgression;
and bring your sacrifices every morning, \add and\add* your tithes
after three years:\f + \fr 4.4  \ft three…: Heb. three years of days\f*
